This package is a bootstrap kit for Graphify and does NOT redistribute
Graphify's source code. It provides documentation, templates, and
configuration helpers for using Graphify in code workspaces.

---

Upstream dependency: Graphify
  Repository: https://github.com/safishamsi/graphify
  Author:     Safi Shamsi
  License:    MIT (Copyright (c) 2026 Safi Shamsi)

The following templates in this package reproduce content generated by the
`graphify claude install` command, included for offline reference and manual
integration. Both are derived from Graphify's MIT-licensed output:

  - templates/claude-md-section.template.md
  - templates/claude-settings-hook.json

For Graphify itself (CLI, library, and skill), refer to the upstream project.
